{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f59b7faa2a","title":"致彭德怀、任弱时电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"028b6f999d","index":0,"year":1936,"month":12,"day":26,"articleId":"f59b7faa2a"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a100337112","type":"paragraph","text":"致彭德怀、任弱时电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"f59b7faa2a"},{"id":"1c297ebfe1","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年12月26日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"f59b7faa2a"},{"id":"ca66142ef9","type":"paragraph","text":"为督促南京撤兵，为准备方一变化，为便利扩大补充野战军，仍应执行原计划，惟不驻咸阳，而照一、二、四方面军次序，驻兴平、武功、扶风、凤翔线，处在南京军大水集团与潼关集团之间，对东北军、西北军则处在其外侧","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"f59b7faa2a"},{"id":"7936700eb1","type":"paragraph","text":"西安已有五方元向庆阳运送。一切购买，不打土豪。驻乡村不驻县城。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"f59b7faa2a"},{"id":"7b6797564b","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东致彭德怀、任强时电的主要内容。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"f59b7faa2a"},{"id":"60726d6d2b","type":"paragraph","text":"21天水集团，指何应钦组织的“讨逆军”的西集团，由顾祝同指挥，集结于天水等地。潼关集团为其东集团，由刘崎指挥，集结于潼关等地","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"f59b7faa2a"}],"page":{"id":"f66ef56247","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"f59b7faa2a","start":221,"end":221}}}},"__N_SSG":true}